{"tid":1670027,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際戰線] 推香港新字上國際?!?!?!?!?!","createTime":"2019-10-23T00:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T04:42:18.000Z","uid":220045,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"36b4bbf36fa081d4d86f2003d480589858c03803","tid":1670027,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T00:50:26.000Z","msg":"大家都知呢幾個月黎中文好多<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新字</span></strong><br />\n例如係以下4個:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/623QrVc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F623QrVc.jpg&h=1698cfaf&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QMASFfd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQMASFfd.jpg&h=b7fd0ed4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1B6KGT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1B6KGT.jpg&h=5df6f323&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7GvWntz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7GvWntz.jpg&h=9e580aae&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n個人覺得呢D字其實真係好有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>時代意義</strong></span></span><br />\n背後亦有好多意思, 一路望個畫面真係出哂黎<br />\n而字呢d野其實係好<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">iconic同symbolic</span></span></strong>, <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">容易令人印象深刻、容易傳播</span></span></strong><br />\n我地又可以藉住呢幾個字<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>好簡單咁就講到比人知香港既基本情況</strong></span></span><br />\n同時外國人近呢10年開始興起左<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">學中文既潮流</span></span></strong><br />\n所以我就係度唸<br />\n如果將呢D字推上國際, 叫外國人學同從中知道更多香港發生咩事<br />\n會唔會算係有gimmick同吸引, 又可以當係國際文宣, 保持國際關注<br />\n我唸到有兩個方法:<br />\n1. 舊酒新瓶 - 整一個<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">challenge</span></strong>鼓勵人學呢D字<br />\n2. 搵方法令<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">國際字典</span></strong> eg. Oxford, Cambridge 將呢D字錄入<br />\n第二個方法做既途徑我暫時淨係搵到可以直接contact D字典, 但唔知人地咁樣會唔會收<br />\n<br />\n以上都只係brainstorm, 大家有咩意見歡迎提出, 一齊集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45db2d77d991cb06b1ebd2c99b5cc565e0cacef5","tid":1670027,"uid":85024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:25:48.000Z","msg":"不失為一個方法"},{"pid":"d3e829b625b6aac165930aa0fddbdf3bbe1ab0d0","tid":1670027,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:29:35.000Z","msg":"諗起城寨佈景仲有幾隻新字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66d9d2a2bb061f17c2d76c03c93d402faf989ce","tid":1670027,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:42:12.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"aae8c72fda614e3c446970041dc41ecdb1cbacdd","tid":1670027,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:44:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f04343aa9a3ca34c9612af3f97e391e87d3fc1","tid":1670027,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:46:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9b03ca599c406f54e73961314c5339e24e9fbdd0","tid":1670027,"uid":196937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:50:26.000Z","msg":"入字典真係要啲時間<br />\nAdd oil HongKongers  我地都用咗好耐先入到國際字山"},{"pid":"7b94276262794b76c0f0839311ed3ed892752c22","tid":1670027,"uid":65408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"字典唔會因為有人造左隻字就會收錄，通常一個字詞係要被廣泛使用一段時間先會令字典編輯確認為有意義。"},{"pid":"e7b94587ba78b4eb59083dc67b441930fc3deb09","tid":1670027,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:58:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span styl